<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別看我這樣，<delay20 />我對自己的房間<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是非常講究的喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你光看就能知道<delay20 />
這房間有哪裡特別講究，<delay8 />
那我的努力就有價值了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這房間裡<delay20 />一邊喝著
<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />一邊讀書，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是我最奢侈的時光喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虧你難得來找我玩，要是我早知道的話，<delay20 />
我就能事先做一些<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
請你吃了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有點擔心家裡是不是<delay20 />
打掃得不夠乾淨<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個，<delay8 />角落的地方<delay20 />
你可別看得太仔細喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有客人來<delay8 />
拜訪自己的房間時，<delay20 />
真讓人有點緊張！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望<delay8 />這麼一來，<delay8 />
能讓你對我<delay20 />
更加了解呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />我們居然可以齊聚一堂，<delay20 />
這還真是難得呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望今天大家<delay8 />都能多聊聊，<delay20 />
加深彼此的情誼喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要好的朋友都<delay8 />圍繞在我身邊，<delay20 />
我能住在<tag a="110" b="33" />上，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太幸運了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊，<delay20 />早知道大家都會過來，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我應該事先多做一些<delay8 />
<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />來了這麼多客人，<delay8 />
我家變得好像觀光景點了呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay8 />好光榮喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想不到居然會有<delay8 />
這麼多客人來，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幸好我有<delay8 />事先打掃過！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊，<delay20 />早知道會有這麼多客人來，<delay8 />
說不定可以舉辦試吃會，<delay8 />請各位嚐嚐<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我新做的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
